  SCIENCE FACTS
============================================================

Domain:  Geology
Topic:   Plate Tectonics
Formula: ~15 major plates on mantle
Note:    Explains earthquakes, volcanoes, mountain formation

Domain:  Geology
Topic:   Age of Earth
Formula: 4.54 billion years
Note:    Determined by radiometric dating of oldest rocks/meteorites

Domain:  Physics
Topic:   Planck's Constant
Formula: h = 6.626×10⁻³⁴ J·s
Note:    Quantum of action; E = hf for photon energy

Domain:  Physics
Topic:   Boyle's Law
Formula: P₁V₁ = P₂V₂
Note:    Pressure and volume inversely proportional at constant T

Domain:  Medicine
Topic:   Germ Theory
Formula: Microorganisms cause disease
Note:    Pasteur/Koch; foundation of modern medicine

